01:42.760 --> 01:44.320
# Just like the... #

01:44.320 --> 01:47.040
Wait a minute, wait.
Aah. Got it?

01:47.040 --> 01:50.280
# Just like the rose, dear

01:50.280 --> 01:53.120
# That's used to the sun

01:53.120 --> 01:55.480
# The petals close, dear

01:55.480 --> 01:58.760
# When summer is done

01:58.760 --> 02:00.600
# And I'm so used to your kisses

02:00.600 --> 02:03.560
