02:03.560 --> 02:05.320
# Used to your loving

02:05.320 --> 02:09.320
# And I don't want to, don't want to,
don't want to, don't want to... #

02:10.680 --> 02:12.840
Well, we ran out of time
on the record

02:12.840 --> 02:15.360
