03:11.600 --> 03:13.880
Listen, you don't drink
too much, Doc.

03:13.880 --> 03:16.720
You got a long drive home.

03:16.720 --> 03:18.880
He's a great guy.

03:18.880 --> 03:22.880
We raced together in the nationals,
1941, '42 and '43.

03:23.040 --> 03:27.000
