03:38.080 --> 03:41.040
Wonderful sport, rowing.

03:41.040 --> 03:42.960
Let me tell you.

03:42.960 --> 03:46.960
You're in a shell,
eight guys and a cox seat.

03:48.560 --> 03:52.560
Each oar has to hit
at exactly the right moment

03:54.560 --> 03:57.800
