roll through every muscle.

04:04.240 --> 04:07.720
You try to push
the water away from you.

04:07.720 --> 04:11.720
After a time, the rhythm clicks
and it's as if you were one body,

04:12.160 --> 04:14.800
driving across the river.

04:14.800 --> 04:18.800
I tell you, there's
nothing like it in the whole world.

04:19.399 --> 04:22.240
Except making love.

04:22.240 --> 04:24.160
What's your sport?

04:24.160 --> 04:26.560
